Natalie Keener.

280
00:20:51,964 --> 00:20:55,058
If there's one word I want to
leave you with today, it's this.

281
00:20:58,070 --> 00:20:59,367
''Glacial''?

282
00:21:00,906 --> 00:21:02,203
Glacial.

283
00:21:02,608 --> 00:21:05,475
Our global must become local.

284
00:21:06,779 --> 00:21:11,546
This company keeps 23 people
